{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f2aabd9b39","title":"关于胡志明去莫斯科和致苏共十九大贺电致刘少奇电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2c41493371","index":0,"year":1952,"month":10,"day":4,"articleId":"f2aabd9b39"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"fb754af3e2","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡志明，当时任越南劳动党中央委员会主席。"},{"id":"2531936bf5","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"原拟的毛泽东致苏共第十九次代表大会的贺电，后来改为中共中央致苏共第十九次代表大会的祝词，由刘少奇在大会上宣读。"},{"id":"e0656a989e","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘少奇在1952年10月3日给中共中央的电报中，建议对毛泽东致苏共第十九次代表大会的贺电稿作几处文字修改，其中一处是在“正确地运用马克思、恩格斯、列宁、斯大林的学说”前面，加上“根据个别国家的具体情况”几个字。毛泽东在刘少奇给中共中央的电报上写了以下批语：“请陆定一同志照此修改，于塔斯社发表大会开幕消息的同时，发表这个贺电。此外，人民日报宜写社论一篇。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cd206ca809","type":"title","text":"关于胡志明去莫斯科和致苏共十九大贺电致刘少奇电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39"},{"id":"fb754af3e2","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39"},{"id":"2531936bf5","type":"paragraph","text":"十月三日来电收到。（一）联共同意胡志明同志秘密去莫斯科，现已定六日乘专机起飞，八日可到莫；（二）同意对贺电的修改文字，惟“个别国家”宜改为“各个国家”","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39"},{"id":"e0656a989e","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39"},{"id":"0821662aa2","type":"paragraph","text":"十月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39"}],"page":{"id":"efe2d25de8","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f2aabd9b39","start":280,"end":280}}}},"__N_SSG":true}